def_cn: 人马宫，人马座(黄道十二宫之一。出生于11月22日至12月21日之间的人属比星座)
def_en: Sagittarius is one of the twelve signs of the zodiac. Its symbol is a creature that is half horse, half man, shooting an arrow. People who are born approximately between the 22nd of November and the 21st of December come under this sign.

def_cn: 出生于人马宫时段的人
def_en: A Sagittarius is a person whose sign of the zodiac is Sagittarius.
